Description: Feature-rich WhatsApp Web client based on Qt WebEngine
 Whatly gives WhatsApp Web a native desktop window with system-tray
 integration, desktop notifications, chat themes, a chat wallpaper, a privacy
 blur, an app lock, a multi-language spell checker and multiple accounts.
 .
 It is an MIT-licensed fork of WhatSie by Keshav Bhatt, and is not affiliated
 with WhatsApp or Meta.
